      <link>https://www.bloomberg.com/news/articles/2025-04-02/a-consultant-who-beat-wall-street-stands-by-bullish-euro-call</link>
      <description><![CDATA[在等待贸易关税对美国经济的影响时，为数不多的少数分析师之一正确预测今年欧元上涨的欧元上涨。]]></description>
